#This file contains instructions on how to run the grabber program.
# How to run this program
First open up grabber.py and modify the url you want to capture a screenshot from

## Pre Requisites:
Ensure you have installed nmap, on your terminal (need root privs), do
`$ sudo pip install python-nmap`

if you have nmap installed without the 'python-' in the beginning, then a conflict
will arise.  remove nmap from your library
`$ sudo pip uninstall nmap`

## Compile and run
on your terminal do
`$ python3 -m grabber.py`

If you have a problem ensure you have all required libraries to run it
